<topic id="associate-ant-validation-scenario">
  <title>Associate a Validation Scenario</title>
  <body>
    <p>You are able to validate Ant build files using a validation scenario. To create a validation
      scenario, select <uicontrol><image href="../img/ValidationConfig16.png" id="image_bvl_55v_sr"
        />Configure Validation Scenario(s)...</uicontrol> from the <uicontrol><image
          href="../img/ValidateDrop.png" id="image_d2m_v5v_sr"/>Validation</uicontrol> toolbar
      drop-down menu or the <menucascade>
        <uicontrol>Document</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Validate</uicontrol>
      </menucascade> menu.</p>
  </body>
</topic>
